data.description: This well-kept custom-built home, located just 5 miles from the award-winning downtown DeLand, offers a unique blend of comfort and functionality. The property boasts an open floor plan designed to facilitate easy movement throughout the home. Some key features include:  Automatic Roll-Up Screen: The two-car garage door is equipped with an automatic roll-up screen, providing privacy while allowing you to enjoy the view.  New Roof and Sliding Door: Recent upgrades include a new roof installed in May 2018 and a new sliding door, enhancing both aesthetics and functionality.  Brick Exterior: The home is enveloped in four sides of brick, adding durability and a classic charm to its exterior.  Under Roof Screen Porch: A screened porch under the roof provides a comfortable space to enjoy the outdoors while being sheltered.  Water Aeration Filtration System: The property features a water aeration filtration system, contributing to water quality.  Detached Shed and Carport: Additional structures include a detached shed and carport, offering extra storage and covered parking.  Mature Landscape: The home is surrounded by a mature landscape, adding to the overall aesthetic appeal.  Storage in the Attic: Ample storage space is available in the attic, providing practical solutions for organization.  Washer and Dryer Included: The convenience of a washer and dryer that remain with the property.  Situated in the Glenwood area, renowned for its biking/walking trail and bird-watching opportunities, the home borders the Lake Woodruff National Wildlife Refuge, a part of the United States National Wildlife Refuge System.  The owner is motivated to sell, making this beautifully maintained home in Glenwood an excellent opportunity for those seeking a comfortable and well-appointed residence in proximity to the charm of downtown DeLand and the natural beauty of Lake Woodruff National Wildlife Refuge. Act quickly, as homes like this one tend not to stay on the market for long.
